#COVID19 VACCINATION DRIVE IN BSF CAMPUS AT BHONDSI ON 08 FEB
A COVID-19 Vaccination Drive was held on 08 Feb 2021 at 95 Bn #BSF Campus, Bhondsi. 

278 BSF personnel were administered COVID-19 #vaccine during this drive. @BSF_India
